      "message": "+1 \nThis should be a call to a function on the resultStore (or another intermediate type) similar to this: \n\nresults, err :\u003d resultStore.Query(runID, sortField, sortOrder)\n...\n\nwhere runID, sortField and sortOrder are extracted from the request and validated as much as possible. I would make sortField and sortOrder strings.",
